data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This enchanting 4-bedroom, 2-bath, one-floor stone house is a masterpiece of timeless design and craftsmanship.  Step inside and be greeted by the open and spacious living room flooded with natural light and a cozy fireplace that will create lasting memories with loved ones on chilly evenings. The heart of this home is the large kitchen, perfect to welcome family and friends over for the holidays. The four generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and privacy.  The attached garage provides convenience and extra storage space for your vehicles and outdoor equipment. Don't miss the opportunity to own this lovely one-floor stone house. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort it has to offer.
